@node Main "Vetex - Documentation"

                               'Vetex' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Vetex' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move two 'X'
shapes, so they are placed on the same tile.  You can only move
these shapes, as well as small coloured squares that are located
on tiles that are linked to an empty tile. When both 'X' shapes
are on the same tile, the 'X' shapes explode and the game board
is completed...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

